<%
  @title = "Admin Tools"
%>

<div style="max-width: 600px;margin: 3em auto;padding:0 1.5em;">
  <dl>
    <dt><a style="color:blue;text-decoration:underline" href="javascript:(function(){window.location=window.location.href.replace('//s3.amazonaws.com/s3', '//www').replace('//s3', '//www').replace(/^http\:/, 'https:').replace(/\/([0-9]+)\//, '/$1-').replace(/\.pdf$/, '.html');})();">Redirect PDF to HTML</a></dt>
    <dd>Sometimes you are linked directly to a DocumentCloud PDF and need to get to the workspace version of the document. Drag the link above to your Bookmarks Bar and click it next time you have a DocumentCloud-hosted PDF open; it will take you to the appropriate page in the workspace.</dd>
  </dl>
</div>
